{
  "text": "Testis cell suspensions from P6 C57BL/6 males were generated as described above and enriched for spermatogonia by centrifugation through a cushion of 32%-39% Percoll (Sigma-Aldrich) and subjected to selection for THY1 using antibodies conjugated to MACS microbeads (CD90.2; Miltenyi Biotec), as described previously [CITATION_1] . THY1 \u00fe , THY1 \u00c0 , and unselected cells (prior to Percoll cushion) were suspended in defined serum-free medium [CITATION_2] and stored on ice until use.",
  "correct_citation": {
